<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a278da3-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7302"><num value="7302">§ 7302.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this chapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id7a278da4-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7302/1"><num value="1" class="bold">(1)</num><heading class="bold"> Fund</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Fund” means the Collaborative Forest Landscape Restoration Fund established by <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s7303/f">section 7303(f) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id7a278da5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7302/2"><num value="2" class="bold">(2)</num><heading class="bold"> Program</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “program” means the Collaborative Forest Landscape Restoration Program established under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s7303/a">section 7303(a) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id7a278da6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7302/3"><num value="3" class="bold">(3)</num><heading class="bold"> Proposal</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “proposal” means a collaborative forest landscape restoration proposal described in <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s7303/b">section 7303(b) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id7a278da7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7302/4"><num value="4" class="bold">(4)</num><heading class="bold"> Secretary</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Secretary” means the Secretary of Agriculture, acting through the Chief of the Forest Service.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id7a278da8-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s7302/5"><num value="5" class="bold">(5)</num><heading class="bold"> Strategy</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “strategy” means a landscape restoration strategy described in <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s7303/b/1">section 7303(b)(1) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id7a278da9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/111/11/tIV/s4002">Pub. L. 111–11, title IV, § 4002</ref>, <date date="2009-03-30">Mar. 30, 2009</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/123/1141">123 Stat. 1141</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
